</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>The interpretation of praying for marriage in the rain is not only about the imminent marriage of the dreamer. It is sometimes associated with the arrival of happy events, pleasant circumstances, and one's rise to a high position in their work, thus obtaining the material and moral appreciation they aspire to. Many experts have stated that praying for rain is a close response to all the prayers and dreams of people in general.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><strong>Dream Interpretation of Praying for Marriage to a Specific Person in the Rain by Ibn Shaheen</strong></h2>
<p>Ibn Shaheen believes that praying for marriage under the rain is like relief from worries and pains, and fairness of the seer's circumstances, and provision of what they want and aspire to. It is also a sign that the dreamer's wishes are about to be fulfilled, and they are ready to be implemented, God willing.</p>
<p>As for a young man or an unmarried girl with a loud voice praying for marriage to a specific person, it is considered a bad omen of falling into a contrived plot or meeting a bad-natured person who can deceive the seer with their hypocrisy. But in reality, they have evil intentions. Therefore, the dreamer should be cautious and avoid dealing with them, so as not to be disliked.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
