<p>Imam Al-Sadiq mentioned many varied interpretations for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-التسول-في-المنام?page=4089" > seeing begging </a> under the rain for marriage. He found that it relates to many life matters that are not limited to marriage. If the dreamer is currently suffering from a chronic illness or serious health problem and sees themselves praying to God in a dream inside a mosque, then this indicates a speedy recovery and healing from all their diseases, by the will of God.</p>
<p>As for those who are suffering from bad financial circumstances or many problems and conflicts in their lives, the dream brings them good tidings of their affairs being facilitated and their situations being rectified, with the end of the obstacles and difficulties that are bothering them and preventing them from succeeding. They will also be very successful in their love life, making them happy and stable.</p>
